TownNPCMood_BestiaryGirl.Content: I feel good. Thanks for asking!
TownNPCMood_BestiaryGirl.NoHome: I can't live in a container. I need a house!
TownNPCMood_BestiaryGirl.FarFromHome: Do I miss home? I have to eat my animals!
TownNPCMood_BestiaryGirl.DislikeCrowded: I worry about a lot of people. I don't want to.
TownNPCMood_BestiaryGirl.HateCrowded: I hate the feeling that happens to all these people!
TownNPCMood_BestiaryGirl.LikeBiome: I love animals, so that {BiomeName} is the best place in the world!
TownNPCMood_BestiaryGirl.DislikeBiome: It is funny that I have instinct!
TownNPCMood_BestiaryGirl.LikeNPC: I like it! I loved it because I was born!
TownNPCMood_BestiaryGirl.DislikeNPC: I don’t like to be so cruel!
TownNPCMood_BestiaryGirl.LikeNPC_Princess: Your subjects are looking for a way to break my curse!

TownNPCMood_BestiaryGirlTransformed.NoHome: Great! I need a house! Now!
TownNPCMood_BestiaryGirlTransformed.FarFromHome: He goes home. I cannot find him.

TownNPCMood_Princess.Content: Everything is under control, my loyal subjects!
TownNPCMood_Princess.NoHome: I don't think I'm staying. Can I urinate?
TownNPCMood_Princess.DislikeCrowded: I know other people can find their faults.
TownNPCMood_Princess.HateCrowded: I like to be surrounded, but I don’t want them to be so happy with abuse.

TownNPCMood_Princess.LoveNPC_Mechanic: I can fix it, I admire it!

TownNPCMood_Princess.LoveNPC_Cyborg: He's cold. I know he knows everything!
